      meaning: |-
        A: Did you see that article in this morning’s paper? About cleansers?
        B: Did they invent a new product of some kind?
        A: No, nothing like that. There was an accident related to cleansers.
        B: An accident...?
        A: A woman was scrubbing hard in her bathroom. When, all of a sudden, she fell over and died.
    tags:
      - iij15
  - id: 4e2df3c8-e457-4386-9811-84f95e40e062
    start: 00:27.3
    end: 00:44.86
    fields:
      transcription: |-
        どうしたんでしょう。
        壁のカビを取る洗剤と、風呂を洗う洗剤を一緒に使ったらしいんです。
