        Husband: Our bathtub’s been getting really dirty.
        Wife: Uh-huh.
        Husband: Were you aware of it?
        Wife: Yeah But I’ve quit using bathroom cleansers.
        Husband: Why?
        Wife: Because they’re scary. They give off fumes.
        Husband: Oh, the compatibility factor.
    tags:
